name: Canadian North's Boeing 737-300 Vancouver to Calgary (Air Transat Wet Lease)
description:
Canadian North is a northern Canadian airline that mostly flies within the Northwest Territories and Nunavut. It’s not often you get to fly with them on a scheduled domestic flight between BC and Alberta though.

Last summer, they wet leased this Boeing 737-300 to Air Transat, and I was able to fly it for a pretty good price by booking it through Transat's website.

See what I thought of Canadian North's 737-300 in this new trip report!
